<h2>v0.24.1</h2>
<h1>You can pipe again</h1>
<p>This point release fixes a regression introduced in <code>v0.24.0</code> in which keyboard and mouse input would be lost when piping and redirecting into a program with default inputs. Special thanks to <a href="https://github.com/pomdtr"><code>@​pomdtr</code></a> for…piping up about the regression.</p>
<ul>
<li>fix: auto-open a TTY when stdin is not a TTY (regression) by <a href="https://github.com/meowgorithm"><code>@​meowgorithm</code></a> in <a href="https://redirect.github.com/charmbracelet/bubbletea/pull/746">charmbracelet/bubbletea#746</a></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/charmbracelet/bubbletea/compare/v0.24.0...v0.24.1">https://github.com/charmbracelet/bubbletea/compare/v0.24.0...v0.24.1</a></p>
